    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and shows clear signs of its age and regular use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dents, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and the driver's seat shows significant wear, though all electronics and climate controls remain functional. It has been a reliable daily driver, but it would benefit from some cosmetic attention and a thorough detailing. Mechanically, it runs and drives, though it doesn't have the smoothness of a newer model.",
