      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being sold as-is. While it remains a reliable daily driver, it shows some clear signs of age and use, including several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door. The interior upholstery has some staining and minor wear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It is a solid option for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a lower price point who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic character and routine maintenance needs.",
