      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this peerless vehicle, preserved in concours-level condition. This specimen exhibits an uncompromising aesthetic and mechanical profile, having been maintained with fastidious attention to detail. It represents a superlative acquisition for the discerning enthusiast seeking a vehicle that retains its original showroom brilliance and peak performance characteristics. Inspections will confirm its status as an exemplary model of its class.",
